      "content": "it doesn't feel like \"imperfect\" though. it feels like i'm just a weight around their necks. i see it in their eyes sometimes. they'd have more opportunities, more peace, if they didn't have to constantly worry about me or deal with the stuff i bring. it's like i'm just polluting their lives.",
